&lt;p&gt;Explore the enchanting world of elephants at Asiaﾕs premier Elephant Camp, as you set out on a once in a lifetime journey with Anantara Golden Triangleﾕs ultimate Discovery Experience unlike any other among Chiang Rai hotels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Book a minimum two night stay to receive a wealth of indulgent rewards. Enjoy irresistible 20% savings on top luxury accommodation and more:&lt;br /&gt;
･ 20% off Rooms&lt;br /&gt;
･ Daily breakfast, lunch and dinner inclusive of a selected range of beverages to be enjoyed at any restaurant, including in-room dining.&lt;br /&gt;
･ One activity per person for every night stayed from a choice of:&lt;br /&gt;
･ Elephant Camp Experience ﾐ Choose from the Elephant Learning Programme, Mahout Training, or Walking with Giants&lt;br /&gt;
･ Spice Spoons ﾐ Anantara cooking school, offering a rich and interactive immersion into Thailandﾕs world famous cuisine&lt;br /&gt;
･ Golden Triangle Discovery Excursion ﾐ Enjoy a tour of rich cultural discovery, complete with your very own car and driver, plus an experienced guide&lt;br /&gt;
･ Beverages (select range of non-alcoholic drinks, house wine, beer and spirits)&lt;br /&gt;
･ Internet access&lt;br /&gt;
･ In-room mini bar&lt;br /&gt;
･ One time visit to the Opium Museum, per person&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please quote your exclusive promotion code DINERS, and show your valid Diners Club International card at check-in to qualify for special rate or Best Flexible Rate at time of check-in will be applied. Additional benefits offered through the promotion are not applicable if making payment with a different card. Please visit anantara.com/dinersoffer for the complete terms and conditions.&lt;/p&gt;

